  "title": "Admin Executive (No Experience Required)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support general administrative tasks and daily operations to ensure smooth workflow.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date records of service providers and clients in the system.</li>\n  <li>Prepare, issue, and input data for invoices with precision and timeliness.</li>\n  <li>Organize, manage, and maintain paperwork and documents related to claims and site progress, ensuring everything is properly filed.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and follow up on work orders and progress reports, providing updates as needed.</li>\n  <li>Assist in handling various formalities, including paperwork related to claims.</li>\n  <li>Undertake any other duties or ad hoc tasks assigned by the supervisor to support team objectives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Possess at least 1 year of relevant experience. Candidates who have no experience but willing to pursue a career in corporate insurance operations are welcomed.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and a good team player</li>\n  <li>Able to multi-task and meet deadlines</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please submit your updated resume in Word format by using the <strong>Apply Now Button.</strong><br>\nWe regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>Email resume to <strong>ken.ng@peopleprofilers.com</strong></p>\n<p>People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil Street, #08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705.<br>\nTel: 6950 9724</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com/\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com</a><br>\nEA License Number: 02C4944<br>\nRegistration Number: R1872398</p>\n<p>Posting Personnel: Ng Jwee Ken</p>\n<p>Ref: 8XY376YV</p>",
